                    <span>I thought this would be a fun way to share "The Night Before Christmas" poem with my 9-year old. The folks who were fascinated by the engineering and awed by the complexity of the pop-ups were my husband and I! This is a keeper, and a great classic Christmas present to give to adults with a sense of whimsy.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">a little disappointing</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
